  <section id="about">
    <h1 class="mx-auto" style="width: 100%; text-align: center;">About this project and limitations</h1>
    <div class="accordion mx-auto" id="accordionExample" style="box-shadow: rgba(100, 100, 111, 0.2) 0px 7px 29px 0px;">
        <div class="accordion-item">
          <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingOne">
            <button class="accordion-button collapsed drop-btn" id="drop" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseOne" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseOne">
              <strong>About this project</strong>
            </button>
          </h2>
          <div id="collapseOne" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="headingOne" data-bs-parent="#accordionExample">
            <div class="accordion-body">
              <strong>Flight Data and more.</strong> Get realtime flights data which is 100% verified and credible. Checkout <a href="https://aviationstack.com/" target="_blank">Aviation API</a>. This API is used by hundreds of flight booking apps and it gives you realtime flight data, history of flight data, airport info, routes info etc. 
              <h2>Features of this website-</h2><br>
              <ul>
                <li>Login and Registration facility via Passport auth, bcrypt and sessions</li>
                <li>Database connectivity using MongoDB Atlas- a cloud database</li>
                <li>Hashed Passwords- Admin or any other authority cannot access your passwords and they are protected</li>
                <li>All routes are protected. Only logged in users can access them</li>
                <li>Realtime flight data around the world of any airport or city</li>
                <li>Simple UI for forms and registrations</li>
                <li>Fast data fetching using express sessions</li>
                <li>Logout facility for users</li>
                <li>See more on readme file of my <a href="https://github.com/AaratBatra" target="_blank">GitHub</a></li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="accordion-item">
          <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingTwo">
            <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseTwo" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseTwo">
              <strong>Limitations</strong> 
            </button>
          </h2>
          <div id="collapseTwo" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="headingTwo" data-bs-parent="#accordionExample">
            <div class="accordion-body">
              <strong>Any and all APIs are chargable.</strong> When I was searching for an ideal api for this project, I came across plenty of websites that provide <strong>"free"</strong> access but they all charge money in USD for even the basic access functions. Luckily AviationStack API allowed access <strong> only for the Current Date Flights and only for one city to another city. </strong>
              <br>
              <h2>This means- </h2>
              <ul>
                <li>Flights data for the current date only</li>
                <li>No realtime booking</li>
                <li>Overall less potential for this website</li>
              </ul>
              <h2>Reason-</h2>
              This project is totally free of cost. No money was invested as this is an internship project for <a href="https://www.codsoft.in/" target="_blank">CodSoft</a> <br>
              Secondly, All hotel apis are paid and do not provide any free access. <br>
              <code>PS- If you have any idea, ping me... I am always ready to scale this project further!</code> 
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </section>
    <br>
    <br>
